<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200806/b854ce157096476189bb57c30727f30f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 笔记本的网格线被错误识别成头发，哈哈哈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200806/3503bc4f18cc4fbaa2fbdc01d6d5b060.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
